(274, '9854030360', '', 'Dear Sir/Mam\r\nNamaskar.\r\nCould you kindly check your Email please?(For face to face training).\r\n1. 2078/07/28 to 08/02 sammako Secondary Mathematics Refresher Training for (Sindhuli,Kavre and Ramechhap) Yeuta palika bata yek jana(Talimko abasar napaunuhuneelai prathamikatama rakhnuhuna).\r\n2. 2078/08/05 to 08/10 samma: ICT Training for Basic level teachers for Sindhuli and Ramechhap only_(Sindhuli ko kamalamai and Dudhauli na pa bahek pratek Palikabata 2 jana and Ramechhap ko pratek palikabata 2 jana) sahavagi chhanaut gari Pathayera sahayog garnu huna anurodh xa. Laptop is compulsory.\r\nIf you have any queries please contact @ Krishna Bhujel(Education Training Center Dhulikhel)- 9851278830.\r\nThank you so much for your Nice Cooperation.\r\nETC,Dhulikhel', '', '2021-11-11 14:26:38', 'krishna'),
