(367, '9848572996', 'ICT Training for Basic Level Teacher', 'Dear Sir/Mam\r\nNamaskar\r\nMiti 2078/08/16 gate dekhi 21 gate samma sanchalan huna lagiraheko aadharvut tahaka teachar haruka lagi ICT Trainingma hajurko Palikabata 2 jana teacher Chhanaut gari pathaidinu huna Binamara Aanurodh xa. Sahavagilai Aaune ra jane Dinko TADA and Sahavagi vayeko dinko Sahavagi Vatta pani bebastha gariyeko huda Tadhaka sirharulai Mansir 15 gate Nai samparkama Pathaunu Vayo Vane Dherai Ramro hunxa. Bistrit Janakariko Lagi Hajurlai Email Pani gariyeko xa.\r\nSamparkako lagi Krishna Bhujel: 9851278830. Dhanayabad.', '', '2021-11-26 14:56:01', 'krishna'),
