(5980, '9844631724', 'TPD Training', '', 'Dear Teacher,\r\nYour name has been confirmed as a participant in a TPD training of Basic level (grade 6-8), English which is going to be held in ETC, Dhulikhel from Baishak 2, 2079. If you will not be able to participate in this training for any reason, please call at this number during office hours: 9841652876 (Ramesh).Please bring a school letter and a laptop. We have already sent letter to your municipalities.Thank you. ', '2022-04-11 14:54:47', 'ramesh'),
