(6114, '9865061139', 'Secondary English TPD', '', 'Dear teacher,\r\nWe have confirmed your name as a participant of Secondary English TPD training which is going to be started from 19th to 29th Asar 2079 at ETC, Dhulikhel. We have sent letters to your local levels (palikas). Please arrive at ETC Dhulikhel at 10 am on 19th Asar with your school or palika letter and a laptop. If any query, please contact at 9841652876 (Ramesh). Thank you see you. ', '2022-06-30 23:04:48', 'ramesh'),
