(5675, '9849677780', 'TPD Training for Basic level(6-8 Mathematics)', '', 'Namaste\r\n2078/12/25 gate dekhi 2079/01/04 samma sanchalan hune TPD Training ko lagi tapaiko name darta vayeko xa. Sambandhit palika ra tapaile upalabdha garaunu vayeko email address ma ETC Dhulikhel ko letter pathaiyeko xa. Kripaya Check garnu hola. chithi napaunuhunele 9851278830 ma email address msg garnuhuna anurodh xa. Training ma aauda samvab bayesamma laptop lyaunuhola. School ko chithi pani lyaunuhola. Talim hune sthan Education Training Center Dhulikhel \r\nUpasthit hune samaya chaitra 25 gate bihana 10 baje.', '2022-04-05 15:55:43', 'krishna'),
